  distro: rhel
  paths:
    cloud_dir: /var/lib/cloud
    templates_dir: /etc/cloud/templates
  ssh_svcname: sshd

# vim:syntax=yaml

=========================================

per instance: the moduel will run only once when a new instance boots, if you launched a new instance from a backup AMI it will run again
per boot: the module will run only once when an instance boots, launching a new instance from a backup AMI will not trigger the module again
per always: the module will run always